<body>

  <% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>

<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="lang-logo">
      <img src="/lang-logo.png">
    </a>
    <h1>Useful hints when working with Wordpress</h1>
    <p>At Vizir we develop applications in a wide variety of languages and platforms. We prefer to develop using JavaScript, Node.js and Ruby. But in some scenarios, we use Wordpress. We put together in this site some hints and useful reminders when working with Wordpress</p>
    <a type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="https://github.com/heroku/node-js-getting-started"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-download"></span> Source on GitHub</a>
  </div>
